originalText.text: This is the school I use to go to when I was in 1st grade up untill 5th grade it was the best school. I miss it so much I am now in 7th grade. I'm going to be in 8th soon. My siblings go to another school no where as good as this school. The teachers are really nice my favorite teacher was Ms.Corvino, I'm sorry other teachers. Every experience I had with her was the best I miss her thank you so much for the best time of my life. The soccer team is the best. GO AMERICA SCORES!.
